title: Interobserver agreement of an ED PoCUS video training dataset of normal appendix and appendicitis in children
details: JW Tsung, M Firnberg, PS DO - The Ultrasound Journal, 2024
abstract: Educational video datasets can be an effective method for training in emergency department (ED) point-of-care ultrasound (PoCUS). A video dataset for normal appendix and appendicitis in children using ED PoCUS images was developed to …
